  "name": "Morrison COU1 — CPB hemolysis credibility assessment (MRL 3)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under cardiopulmonary bypass (CPB) conditions. This package re-evaluates the COU at Model Risk Level 3 following an expanded decision scope that increases model influence from Medium to High. Twelve of thirteen credibility factors are fully assessed and meet required levels. The Equivalency of input parameters factor is documented as not requiring assessment because the validation experiments used the same nominal boundary conditions as the COU; however, the factor carries factorStatus 'not-assessed' rather than 'not-applicable', leaving a gap that materially weakens credibility at MRL 3.",
