      "acceptanceCriteria": "Grid convergence must be demonstrated; GCI < 5% on quantities of interest.",
      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study performed (coarse 4.2M, medium 8.7M, fine 17.1M cells). GCI on hemolysis index: 2.1% (fine-to-medium). GCI on peak shear stress: 3.8%. Both within the 5% acceptance threshold. Richardson-extrapolated solution used for production runs."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
